Introduction

Jung Youngbin is a South Korean singer. He was the leader, main dancer and lead vocalist of the boy group LUMINOUS.

He was first known as a participant in the hit survival show Produce X 101 in 2019, however he was eliminated in episode 5 after ranking in 68th place.

Youngbin made his official debut as the leader of the boy group LUMINOUS on September 9, 2021, with their first mini album "Youth".
